<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling">
  <head>
    <styling>
      <style xml:id="defaultFont" tts:fontFamily="Arial" tts:fontSize="100%" tts:color="white"/>
    </styling>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div xml:lang="en">
      <p begin="00:00:01.000" end="00:00:03.500">Hello, my name is Sarah.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:04.000" end="00:00:06.200">Welcome to the show tonight.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:07.000" end="00:00:09.800">Sarah: I've been waiting for this moment.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:10.500" end="00:00:12.000">The music starts playing softly.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:13.000" end="00:00:15.500">Sarah looks at the camera and smiles.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:16.000" end="00:00:18.800">"This is going to be amazing," she says.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:19.500" end="00:00:21.000">The audience cheers loudly.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.000" end="00:00:24.500">Sarah: Thank you all for coming.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.000" end="00:00:27.200">We have a special guest tonight.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:28.000" end="00:00:30.800">Please welcome John to the stage!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:31.500" end="00:00:33.000">John walks out waving to the crowd.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:34.000" end="00:00:36.500">John: Hello everyone! Great to be here.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:37.000" end="00:00:39.200">Sarah: We're so glad you could make it.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:40.000" end="00:00:42.800">John: I wouldn't miss it for the world.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.500" end="00:00:45.000">The lights dim slightly.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:46.000" end="00:00:48.500">Sarah: Let's begin with your new project.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.000" end="00:00:51.200">John: Yes, it's been quite a journey.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:52.000" end="00:00:54.800">John: We started working on it last year.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:55.500" end="00:00:57.000">Sarah nods encouragingly.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:58.000" end="00:01:00.500">John: The team has been incredible.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:01.000" end="00:01:03.200">Sarah: Tell us about the challenges.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:04.000" end="00:01:06.800">John: Well, there were many obstacles.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:07.500" end="00:01:09.000">John pauses thoughtfully.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:10.000" end="00:01:12.500">John: But we never gave up hope.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.000" end="00:01:15.200">Sarah: That's truly inspiring.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:16.000" end="00:01:18.800">The audience applauds enthusiastically.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:19.500" end="00:01:21.000">Sarah: Thank you, John.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:22.000" end="00:01:24.500">John: Thank you for having me.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:25.000" end="00:01:27.200">Sarah: We'll be right back after the break.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:28.000" end="00:01:30.800">Stay tuned for more exciting content!</p>
      <p begin="00:01:31.500" end="00:01:33.000">[Music plays]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:34.000" end="00:01:36.500">Sarah: Welcome back, everyone.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:37.000" end="00:01:39.200">John: It's great to be back.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:40.000" end="00:01:42.800">Sarah: Let's continue our discussion.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:43.500" end="00:01:45.000">John smiles warmly.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:46.000" end="00:01:48.500">John: I have a surprise for everyone.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:49.000" end="00:01:51.200">Sarah: Oh really? Do tell!</p>
      <p begin="00:01:52.000" end="00:01:54.800">John: We're launching a new initiative.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:55.500" end="00:01:57.000">The crowd murmurs with excitement.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.000" end="00:02:00.500">John: It's called "Project Tomorrow."</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.000" end="00:02:03.200">Sarah: That sounds wonderful!</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.000" end="00:02:06.800">John: We'll share more details soon.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:07.500" end="00:02:09.000">Sarah claps her hands.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.000" end="00:02:12.500">Sarah: I can't wait to hear more.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.000" end="00:02:15.200">John: Trust me, it's worth the wait.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:16.000" end="00:02:18.800">The audience cheers once more.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:19.500" end="00:02:21.000">Sarah: That's all for today.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:22.000" end="00:02:24.500">John: Thank you all so much!</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.000" end="00:02:27.200">Sarah: See you next time!</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.000" end="00:02:30.800">[Applause and music]</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
